{"type": "article", "id": 34828, "title": "单管辉光钟，显示数字的方式有点特别｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-11-23T23:29:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 21587, "name": "Muuto"}, {"id": 30564, "name": "OTOTO"}, {"id": 35161, "name": "Craft Combine"}, {"id": 35162, "name": "Johan van Hengel"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 110, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161123224442sPI2zKwpb5laDWAd.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>SWANKY by OTOTO</h3><p>那个以设计创意小物闻名的以色列工作室 <a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OTOTO</a> 带来了一件或许会让你感到眼熟的新作品，天鹅造型的长柄勺 SWANKY。和之前深受欢迎的<a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/collections/kitchen/products/nessie\" rel=\"nofollow\">尼斯湖怪勺</a>不同的是，天鹅勺圆润光滑的底部让它可以在桌面上像不倒翁一样摇摆，可以成为一件优雅的厨房摆设。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/539177001/swankytm-the-floating-ladle\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 17 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224818QevfAPuXBUq4WMgH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016112322481985XKFA3VMqka60nu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705882\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224818AYW1aKJgp0Hkqvsz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.602941\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224819QAuNiP0ETYpWhj9t.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.872059\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Vue</h3><p>来自美国的设计团队 Vue 以“融入日常生活”为核心研发了一款从外观上来看和普通眼镜没有区别的同名智能眼镜，让人们在享受科技带来的各种便利时不会产生突兀的感觉。为了做到这一点，这款眼镜也舍弃了需要安装镜头的拍摄功能，主打语音服务。这款眼镜采用的是骨传导技术，只要在镜框上进行简单的触控，不用拿出手机就能完成各类操作。除此之外，眼镜还内置了感应器可以记录行走步数和运动时间等数据。如果用户不小心忘记 Vue 放在哪里了，可以通过配套的软件找到它。团队还专门为 Vue 打造了一个收纳盒，它同时也是眼镜专用的无线充电器。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/vue/vue-your-everyday-smart-glasses\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 179 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224752GpAY3DCoemz7HVFT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.670588\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611232247523rugPIRZ4LSvyqdH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224753lWwBzc5tGYRVmQ3k.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224752E6Nayh1gKDPUMe9j.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224752B08e5DvOWZdRxTLF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.710294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Blub Keo by Duncan Hellmers</h3><p>来自澳大利亚的 Duncan Hellmers 一直都想尝试制作一台造型美观且使用方便的辉光钟，为此他花费了两年的时间研发了这款通过 mini USB 接口充电的 Blub Keo。虽然采用的是单个辉光管，但并不妨碍多个数字的显示，比如早上 7:35 就会根据顺序显示 0735 这四个数字。根据 Hellmers 的介绍，用户可以对 Blub Keo 进行远程操控，除了时间和温度的显示之外，还有闹铃、睡眠模式、背光功能。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/767936743/blub-keo-a-supersized-usb-powered-tube-clock\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 399 澳元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224646d1IzeoFCfMcqGmnB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224648ncGDIMa5VLBYdowf.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224645C7MgNRlEG486Yvup.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.791176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224645c5eOaPwD4giIFoW6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.605882\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224645oLISQOVtZkE1Wgn2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.605882\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>FOLDED by Johan van Hengel</h3><p>荷兰设计师 <a href=\"http://www.johanvanhengel.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Johan van Hengel</a> 最近为北欧设计品牌 <a href=\"http://www.muuto.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">MUUTO</a> 设计了一款名为 FOLDED 的墙面收纳系统。这些置物架的造型相当简洁，都是采用单张金属片弯曲而成的。这也赋予了置物架一种类似信封的效果，可以将不同物品分开放置。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224716nCEcoYxNKQfW5qZl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334724\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224715gu2LF1WH7iGB8NbA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224715Ds05wVcPeGyJuYh9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224716wAXzKnbgZNTIcR7m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224716JLfye23n0xc1VGvN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.512500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224715UmWHtld6PDqZTRnE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.511719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Piece Furniture by Craft Combine</h3><p>你见过用画拼成的家具吗？韩国鸿益大学 <a href=\"http://www.craftcombine.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Craft Combine</a> 设计工作室带来了这套名为 <a href=\"http://www.craftcombine.com/piece-furniture\" rel=\"nofollow\">Piece Furniture</a> 的迷你家具系列，通常状态下，这三幅以山、海和城市为主题的作品以拼图的形式收纳在画框中。每一套拼图都可以取下，通过简单的拼接组成一件迷你家具。Craft Combine 的四位设计师们，希望利用相框作为媒介，借此探索图像和产品之间的关系。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224630RW2345ibeEdOZjXA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224630oRFd5py6VT7mYvxn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224630DmtfLaJBipqhI2SK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224630pyXqQ34btDP6xTM8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Marcareux by Luminous Design Group</h3><p>希腊的意面品牌 Marcareux 委托 Luminous Design Group 为其设计了一套用巧妙的方式传递出产品信息的包装。品牌的 logo 出现在包装正面的右侧，其中一部分被特意镂空，让顾客可以直接看到产品。左侧是一条延伸到包装背面的标签，上面标记了意面的种类、烹饪时间等信息。在包装的侧面部分，标签上也有一道和正面类似的镂空处理，形状刚好和意面吻合。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224534M10X5YWAH7jmZbT6.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728125\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224537SMF2AoKqLNcnj5Dv.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728125\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161123224539cVmu875JQOENpUjY.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.543750\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611232245388eYsMFKWXNkmlxE3.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.217656\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611232245375DsgyxvJCQt7cLq8.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.570000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>"}